  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/8e6c5876cf30ad1f99700c1e545c9ed9.webp?t=1716236665\" width=616 height=28 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome! You are dead.</h2><br>When you are neither good enough for heaven nor bad enough for hell, then you are destined for an eternity in limbo...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/1859e767e1d0eadb6dd54650f350959d.avif?t=1716236665\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br><br>You can spend the rest of your unlife in bureaucratic madness or you can have a purposeful afterlife.<br>Join the reaper academy, get trained to be a reaper and help the system.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/4afa0b67e7a410f05b61123034dd3de0.webp?t=1716236665\" width=616 height=28 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Join Now!</h2>In our course you will learn to <strong>capture the souls</strong> of the recently dead,<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/ebf07d8dbe29cb06c0fde477ac307fd4.poster.avif?t=1716236665\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/ebf07d8dbe29cb06c0fde477ac307fd4.webm?t=1716236665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/ebf07d8dbe29cb06c0fde477ac307fd4.mp4?t=1716236665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You will train the necessary <strong>skills</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/a3c6aab9f856e7e217db98f7c380362d.poster.avif?t=1716236665\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/a3c6aab9f856e7e217db98f7c380362d.webm?t=1716236665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/a3c6aab9f856e7e217db98f7c380362d.mp4?t=1716236665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>regardless of the <strong>difficulties</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/16a9203db482db1c47e727922e8877df.poster.avif?t=1716236665\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/16a9203db482db1c47e727922e8877df.webm?t=1716236665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/16a9203db482db1c47e727922e8877df.mp4?t=1716236665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The <strong>obstacles</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/ea6ce0a0ca0809c861325a6f07e08841.poster.avif?t=1716236665\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/ea6ce0a0ca0809c861325a6f07e08841.webm?t=1716236665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/ea6ce0a0ca0809c861325a6f07e08841.mp4?t=1716236665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The<strong> laser rays</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/f7d47f43e8bd736a43605d53e9504763.poster.avif?t=1716236665\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/f7d47f43e8bd736a43605d53e9504763.webm?t=1716236665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/f7d47f43e8bd736a43605d53e9504763.mp4?t=1716236665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/4afa0b67e7a410f05b61123034dd3de0.webp?t=1716236665\" width=616 height=28 /></span><br>Upgrade the <strong>50 levels</strong> to graduate and get your reaper's diploma. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/abfb2fa9226754071d1eedba2e192c37.webp?t=1716236665\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/abfb2fa9226754071d1eedba2e192c37.poster.avif?t=1716236665\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=135 /></picture></span><br><br><strong>Work for the system.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848880/extras/5f14a6eee9c9c35071d95e73340aa083.webp?t=1716236665\" width=616 height=35 /></span>",
